# PCOS Metabolic Risk Calculator

This web-based tool predicts the risk of **metabolic syndrome in women with PCOS** using clinical parameters.

## 💡 Features

- Simple user interface (Streamlit)
- Inputs: BMI, Waist Circumference, Triglycerides, HDL, Fasting Blood Sugar
- Outputs: Risk estimate (Low / Moderate / High)

## 🚀 Live Demo

👉 [Try the app here](https://suman1975cell-pcos-metabolic-cal.streamlit.app)

## 🛠️ How to Run Locally

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run app.py
